{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Psa|94","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","chapter":94,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":1,"text":"Lord, God of vengeance — God of vengeance, shine!","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":2,"text":"Rise up, Judge of the earth; repay the proud what they deserve.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":3,"text":"Lord, how long will the wicked — how long will the wicked celebrate?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":4,"text":"They pour out arrogant words; all the evildoers boast.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":5,"text":"Lord, they crush your people; they oppress your heritage.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":6,"text":"They kill the widow and the resident alien and murder the fatherless.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":7,"text":"They say, “The Lord doesn’t see it. The God of Jacob doesn’t pay attention.”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":8,"text":"Pay attention, you stupid people! Fools, when will you be wise?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":9,"text":"Can the one who shaped the ear not hear, the one who formed the eye not see?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":10,"text":"The one who instructs nations, the one who teaches mankind knowledge — does he not discipline?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":11,"text":"The Lord knows the thoughts of mankind; they are futile.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":12,"text":"Lord, how happy is anyone you discipline and teach from your law","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":13,"text":"to give him relief from troubled times until a pit is dug for the wicked.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":14,"text":"The Lord will not leave his people or abandon his heritage,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":15,"text":"for the administration of justice will again be righteous, and all the upright in heart will follow it.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Psa:94:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Psa","bookOrder":18,"chapter":94,"verse":16,"text":"Who stands up for 